118
00:07:50,910 --> 00:07:52,309
Ini bukan hanya soal uang!

119
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:56,879
Kamu benar.

120
00:07:57,309 --> 00:07:58,850
Aku telah salah menilaimu.

121
00:07:59,150 --> 00:08:00,749
